            "value": "Individuals aged between 18 and 65 years old; - Alcohol-dependent* patients that have been weaned for at least a week (according to DSM-IV criteria); - Control subjects exposed to alcohol consumption but who do not fulfil dependence criteria*; - Individuals that are first-degree relatives of an alcohol-dependent person with no personal dependence criterion*.  "
